Package: sparseNumeric
Title: Sparse Numeric Vector Class and Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mason", "Reed", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements an S4 sparse numeric vector class with methods for
    arithmetic, plotting, computing means and norms, and standardizing vectors
    without materializing dense representations unless necessary.
